scenes.description: Continuation of the performance of 'Maze Town'.
Performance of the song 'Mashou Shoujo' with Takanashi Kiara.

subtitles.original: 日の光降る朝
subtitles.english: The morning when the sunlight falls

subtitles.original: 期待みたいね
subtitles.english: It's like anticipation, isn't it?

subtitles.original: 重い扉の奥で
subtitles.english: Behind the heavy doors

subtitles.original: さあ その時を待ってる
subtitles.english: Come, I'm waiting for that moment

subtitles.original: いつまでも繋がる
subtitles.english: Connected forever

subtitles.original: 永遠なんてない 誰が決めた？
subtitles.english: Who decided there's no such thing as eternity?

subtitles.original: 時も命も 飛び越え
subtitles.english: Leaping over both time and life

subtitles.original: 信じよう
subtitles.english: Let's believe

subtitles.original: Maze Town Maze Town 逃れられないわ
subtitles.english: Maze Town, Maze Town, you can't escape

subtitles.original: 迷い続ける 幾多の魂
subtitles.english: Many souls continue to wander

subtitles.original: 何千もの雨風 乗り越えて
subtitles.english: Overcoming thousands of rain and wind

subtitles.original: 守ってきた
subtitles.english: I have protected it

subtitles.original: Maze Town どんなに暗い場所だろうと
subtitles.english: Maze Town, no matter how dark the place may be

subtitles.original: 進み続ける まだ見ぬ未来も
subtitles.english: I will keep moving forward, even into an unseen future

subtitles.original: 大切なもの 壊さぬように
subtitles.english: So as not to break the things important to me

subtitles.original: 足音に耳 澄ます
subtitles.english: I listen closely to the footsteps

subtitles.original: そこにいるのは 誰？ 誰？ 誰？
subtitles.english: Who is there? Who? Who?

subtitles.original: 鏡越し 不気味な音で Let you know
subtitles.english: Through the mirror, with an eerie sound, let you know

subtitles.original: この場所へ 私たちの棲み処
subtitles.english: To this place, our dwelling

subtitles.original: ないはずの 黒い影うごめけ
subtitles.english: Black shadows that shouldn't exist, wriggle

subtitles.original: 不気味なシルエット
subtitles.english: An eerie silhouette

subtitles.original: 確かにあるもの
subtitles.english: Something that certainly exists

subtitles.original: 離さない 未来まで
subtitles.english: I won't let go, until the future

subtitles.original: 信じてきた この想い ここに
subtitles.english: The feelings I've believed in are here

subtitles.original: Maze Town Maze Town 離れられないわ
subtitles.english: Maze Town, Maze Town, I can't leave

subtitles.original: 回り続ける 記憶とこの場所
subtitles.english: Memories and this place keep spinning

subtitles.original: 僅かな時間と 思い出も
subtitles.english: Even the small amount of time and memories

subtitles.original: 守っていくから
subtitles.english: I will go on protecting them

subtitles.original: Maze Town 明けない夜を飛び越えて
subtitles.english: Maze Town, leaping over the night that never ends

subtitles.original: 今蘇る 彷徨う魂
subtitles.english: Wandering souls now come back to life

subtitles.original: 境界線 曖昧に溶け出してく
subtitles.english: The boundaries are starting to blur and melt

subtitles.original: 心に耳を当てて
subtitles.english: Place your ear to your heart

subtitles.original: そばにいるのは 誰？
subtitles.english: Who is by your side?

subtitles.original: さあ 動き出した
subtitles.english: Come, it has started moving

subtitles.original: 永遠に 踊り続けましょう
subtitles.english: Let's keep dancing forever

subtitles.original: 巡る 巡る 時を乗り越えて
subtitles.english: Overcoming the spinning, revolving time

subtitles.original: 進み続ける 私は変わらず
subtitles.english: I continue to move forward, unchanged

subtitles.original: どんな日でも 守りたいものを 守ってきた 今
subtitles.english: No matter the day, I've protected what I wanted to protect, and now...

subtitles.original: 動き出した
subtitles.english: ...it has started moving

subtitles.english: Who is there? Who? Who?

subtitles.original: あなたの逃げ場は私 魅惑が手引きする
subtitles.english: I am your refuge; fascination will guide you

subtitles.original: ある夜に あなたの居場所はない 奈落はない
subtitles.english: On a certain night, you have no place, there is no abyss

subtitles.original: 朽ちるまで 光りましょう ましょう
subtitles.english: Let us shine until we rot, shall we?

subtitles.original: 魔性少女
subtitles.english: Bewitching Girl

subtitles.original: Lyrics, Music: なきそ
subtitles.english: Lyrics, Music: Nakiso

subtitles.original: はじめましてのキスをしましょう
subtitles.english: Let's share a first-time kiss

subtitles.original: 味気ないだけの ドラマと違う 私は毒気
subtitles.english: Different from a boring drama, I am poisonous

subtitles.original: まるで運命の糸を 結びつける
subtitles.english: It's as if I'm tying the thread of fate

subtitles.original: お遊び 大胆に抱きしめてあげる ほら虜
subtitles.english: Just for play, I'll hold you boldly, look, you're captivated

subtitles.original: 奪っちゃった 心ごと 恨み言を どうぞさあ どうぞ どうぞ
subtitles.english: I've stolen your heart, go ahead with your grudges, please, come on

subtitles.original: 魔法のような超常現象 誰もが夢中 愛してる
subtitles.english: A supernatural phenomenon like magic, everyone is obsessed, I love you
